1
00:01:25,260 --> 00:01:28,130
[Whispers of Fate]

2
00:01:28,490 --> 00:01:29,950
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:30,870 --> 00:01:31,920
Here and now,

4
00:01:32,350 --> 00:01:33,310
no one

5
00:01:33,310 --> 00:01:34,910
will meddle in your affairs.

6
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:35,840
You

7
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:37,070
will die today. There's no doubt about it.

8
00:01:37,070 --> 00:01:38,200
I'm making this my business today,

9
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,000
like it or not!

10
00:01:42,590 --> 00:01:43,720
A traitor of Yanmen.

11
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:48,070
How dare you silence a witness
right before my eyes.

12
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,850
When those noble clans play dirty,

13
00:01:49,850 --> 00:01:51,979
they make my den of thieves look clean.

14
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:54,300
Don't worry, Mr. Feng—

15
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:55,930
I've got your back.

16
00:01:58,450 --> 00:01:59,450
Cloud?

17
00:01:59,970 --> 00:02:01,770
Well, well. It's your choice,

18
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,590
but you're just

19
00:02:03,940 --> 00:02:05,400
choosing your own poison.

20
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:09,120
Since

21
00:02:09,660 --> 00:02:11,120
you're all so eager to die,

22
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:13,760
I'll make sure

23
00:02:13,790 --> 00:02:15,580
you perish together today.

24
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,320
Kill them all!

25
00:03:21,630 --> 00:03:22,560
Are you alright?

26
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:26,560
What's going on?

27
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:28,400
Clearly, Jiang Qingyu

28
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,560
has long since bribed everyone here

29
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,160
to ensure Mr. Feng's demise.

30
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,360
Our priority now

31
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,810
is to get out of here.

32
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,560
Thinking of leaving?

33
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,590
I've gambled everything

34
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,990
to get this opportunity.

35
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:44,470
Vice-Chief Jiang,
are you certain about this?

36
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:45,750
Once this deal is done,

37
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,650
you'll have nothing left.

38
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:49,480
You're mistaken, Chief.

39
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:51,079
If this deal succeeds,

40
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:52,900
I will have everything.

41
00:03:53,190 --> 00:03:54,750
But this place is shrouded in thick mist—

42
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:56,810
I can't locate the gate of life at all.

43
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,560
Indeed, the Mist Formation of Buhuan Tower

44
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,280
makes it

45
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:03,360
difficult to spot the gate of life
with the naked eye.

46
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,430
However, after years

47
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:06,230
of cultivating the Yulan Sword,

48
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,000
I can trace the flow of air

49
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,120
to find the gate of life—

50
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,520
it shouldn't be too hard.

51
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:13,590
You really are both reliable and sharp.

52
00:04:13,590 --> 00:04:14,590
Which way do we go?

53
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:24,410
Over there.

54
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,380
Let's move.

55
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,480
One,

56
00:04:55,270 --> 00:04:55,800
two,

57
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,159
three.

58
00:05:02,970 --> 00:05:04,040
Soon, you'll

59
00:05:04,130 --> 00:05:05,890
all die here.

60
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,240
Once that happens,

61
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:14,050
no one will ever trace the truth
behind Cheng's death again.

62
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:20,520
Judging by the sound of the wind,

63
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,800
the Floating Abyss

64
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:24,130
must be sinking into the depths
of the sea.

65
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,000
Follow me—

66
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,000
I'll lead you out.

67
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:30,870
It's you!

68
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,060
Jiang Qingyu,

69
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,680
you poisoned Jiang Cheng,

70
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,490
all because Liu Yan manipulated you.

71
00:05:35,490 --> 00:05:37,890
Greed led you to invite evil
upon yourself.

72
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,120
How pathetic.

73
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:41,470
In this jianghu, power reigns supreme.

74
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:43,040
Once I ascend to that position,

75
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,920
who would dare deny

76
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,720
that the loyal and true-hearted
leader of Yanmen Sect

77
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,920
stands for righteousness?

78
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:49,450
You twist minds
and reverse cause and effect.

79
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,380
After them!

80
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,920
It's Cheng's goose.

81
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:22,390
Foxy Tang,

82
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,210
what are you doing here?

83
00:06:25,170 --> 00:06:27,100
And you've captured Jiang Qingyu?

84
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,270
Thank you, Mr. Tang, for sparing his life.

85
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:41,630
This man is a key suspect wanted

86
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:43,760
by the Central Plains Sword Alliance.

87
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:45,670
Right now,

88
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,390
our priority is to get out of here.

89
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,390
Which way do we go?

90
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:49,270
Here.

91
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,770
This way—

92
00:06:51,490 --> 00:06:52,430
the exit is over here.

93
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:52,870
Wait.

94
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:58,550
Foxy Tang,

95
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,810
we need to leave now.

96
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,040
Indeed, Mr. Tang.

97
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,310
This place is sinking fast.

98
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:03,440
The longer we delay,

99
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,240
the harder it will be

100
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,900
for even me to locate the exit.

101
00:07:07,740 --> 00:07:08,340
Is that so?

102
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:14,490
An exit—

103
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,240
or

104
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:17,100
a one-way path to the underworld?

105
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,070
Mr. Tang,

106
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,980
you don't trust me?

107
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,150
I trust Feng Chuanxiang.

108
00:07:24,180 --> 00:07:24,780
But are you

109
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,000
really Feng Chuanxiang?

110
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:44,560
Foxy Tang!

111
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:48,950
Mr. Tang,

112
00:07:50,450 --> 00:07:51,180
why?

113
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:54,720
It's because the real Feng Chuanxiang

114
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,680
has been dead

115
00:08:02,570 --> 00:08:03,620
for half a year.

116
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,270
He was killed by Jiang Cheng

117
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:07,170
on the very night
of his alleged disappearance—

118
00:08:07,170 --> 00:08:08,620
slain by Jiang Cheng
in a poison-induced haze,

119
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:10,750
unable to distinguish hallucination

120
00:08:11,370 --> 00:08:12,490
from reality.

121
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,320
So that's what happened.

122
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,870
Is that true,

123
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,190
Mr. Feng?

124
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:30,330
Tang Lici,

125
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:32,000
as expected—

126
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:35,000
you are a worthy adversary of Master.

127
00:09:04,970 --> 00:09:06,500
Let me reintroduce myself.

128
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,240
I am

129
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,080
Hua Wuyan

130
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:11,520
of the Fengliu Shop.

131
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,840
Emissary Hua,

132
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,150
you promised me—

133
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,480
if I helped you

134
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,510
lure Tang Lici and the others here

135
00:09:21,510 --> 00:09:23,310
so you could eliminate them all,

136
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,390
y-you would secure my position

137
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:27,030
as the leader of Yanmen Sect.

138
00:09:27,790 --> 00:09:29,590
You must not go back on your word.

139
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:30,360
Silence!

140
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,590
If I may ask,

141
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:34,550
Mr. Tang,

142
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,480
when did you first realize

143
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,940
I wasn't Feng Chuanxiang?

144
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:40,000
The wind brushes
through reed-covered lands;

145
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:42,000
the moon shatters over Mount Huaxi.

146
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,390
Mr. Tang,

147
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:44,920
pleased to meet you.

148
00:09:45,290 --> 00:09:46,490
I am Feng Chuanxiang.

149
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:48,870
The wind brushes
through reed-covered lands;

150
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:50,720
the moon shatters over Mount Huaxi.

151
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,720
A western sword stroke sweeps afar;

152
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,780
wild geese cross miles of riverbank.

153
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,390
Mr. Tang,

154
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,370
is something wrong?

155
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,130
You didn't recognize the jade pendant,

156
00:10:05,130 --> 00:10:06,910
nor did you understand the poem.

157
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:07,600
The answer

158
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,480
was clear from the start.

159
00:10:10,670 --> 00:10:12,790
So, I gave myself away

160
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,520
at the very beginning, did I?

161
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:16,580
He used the Hao family massacre as bait—

162
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:18,270
first dragging Zhong Chunji's

163
00:10:18,270 --> 00:10:19,600
Central Plains Sword Alliance
into the mess,

164
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,720
then exploiting Jiang Qingyu's greed

165
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,280
for the Jiang Sect leadership

166
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,880
to stir up chaos within Yanmen.

167
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,830
Had I failed to see through this scheme,

168
00:10:25,830 --> 00:10:28,230
I would have been hunted
across the jianghu

169
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:28,960
and forced

170
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:31,510
to bring Chi Yun and Zhong Chunji

171
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:33,150
to the Shisan Tower

172
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,820
to bargain with the Chief—

173
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:36,650
there, I would have been compelled

174
00:10:36,650 --> 00:10:38,910
to speak with my own lips
and reveal the secret from years past.

175
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:40,120
Four years apart,

176
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,240
and his methods remain

177
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:44,160
as clumsy as your disguise.

178
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:46,670
How dare you disrespect the Master!

179
00:11:00,950 --> 00:11:02,280
Did he not tell you

180
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:14,260
to flee

181
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:15,800
at the sight of me?

182
00:11:18,890 --> 00:11:20,150
If you knew

183
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:21,870
I was an impostor from the start,

184
00:11:21,870 --> 00:11:23,630
yet still played along

185
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:31,270
and let these baits into the pond,

186
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:32,720
it was all

187
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,980
to trace the Master's scheme back to him.

188
00:11:35,060 --> 00:11:35,820
Mr. Tang,

189
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,630
have you considered

190
00:11:37,890 --> 00:11:38,840
that if this move

191
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,240
had gone wrong,

192
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:41,320
their lives…

193
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,200
My time is precious.

194
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,790
I have no interest

195
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:45,970
in wasting more words on you.

196
00:11:45,970 --> 00:11:46,720
Finding Liu Yan

197
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,000
is my true objective—

198
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:49,510
nothing else

199
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:52,190
matters to me.

200
00:11:56,770 --> 00:11:58,930
Just as the Master said—

201
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:01,080
devoid of sentiment,

202
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:03,270
driven only by cold self-interest.

203
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:06,920
It seems

204
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,660
he didn't teach you

205
00:12:09,460 --> 00:12:10,910
when to beg for mercy.

206
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,570
Knowing when to beg me for mercy

207
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:14,860
would have been wise.

208
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,240
Take me to him.

209
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:30,720
Chi Yun.

210
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:41,230
It's Liu Yan's doing.

211
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:09,630
He's mine.

212
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:11,480
Is that so?

213
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:28,270
Mr. Tang!

214
00:13:33,770 --> 00:13:35,000
I am Cao Wufang.

215
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:36,790
Tang Lici,

216
00:13:37,210 --> 00:13:38,540
you've grown careless.

217
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,590
A sword through the heart—

218
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,200
a fatal wound.

219
00:13:49,510 --> 00:13:50,150
Foolish.

220
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:03,500
Two souls in one body—

221
00:14:03,730 --> 00:14:05,000
when one dies, the other lives;

222
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,280
when one lives, the other dies.

223
00:14:06,280 --> 00:14:07,880
To think such a constitution

224
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:09,710
truly exists in this world.

225
00:14:10,870 --> 00:14:12,350
You think I'm a monster?

226
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:15,790
The Master said

227
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:17,460
you're a monster too.

228
00:14:19,180 --> 00:14:20,940
Monster against monster—

229
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,350
a perfect match.

230
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:26,840
Mr. Tang,

231
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:28,730
can monsters

232
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:31,270
even understand human emotions?

233
00:14:39,830 --> 00:14:40,880
Go tell Liu Yan

234
00:14:41,580 --> 00:14:42,840
that his petty tricks

235
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,700
are no match for Tang Lici.

236
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,360
I, Tang Lici,

237
00:14:47,420 --> 00:14:49,150
am second to none under heaven.

238
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:54,550
If he wishes to settle our score,

239
00:14:54,810 --> 00:14:56,010
let him come himself.

240
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:57,530
Now get lost.

241
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,050
Tang Lici,

242
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:19,440
if you wish to see the Master,

243
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:21,220
follow the trail of the Evil Pill.

244
00:15:21,220 --> 00:15:22,600
But first, you and your friends

245
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,370
shall enjoy this little extra gift

246
00:15:24,370 --> 00:15:25,680
he prepared for you.

247
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:29,840
What do we do?

248
00:16:30,270 --> 00:16:31,700
The flames are closing in on all sides!

249
00:16:31,700 --> 00:16:32,340
Foxy Tang,

250
00:16:32,870 --> 00:16:34,470
stop holding back—bring out

251
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:35,790
your contingency plan now.

252
00:16:35,790 --> 00:16:36,990
Empty-handed as I am,

253
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,610
I have no contingency plan.

254
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:40,730
Empty-handed—

255
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:45,050
Aren't you afraid
of turning into a roasted fox?

256
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,240
Mr. Tang,

257
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:14,230
after receiving word from Miss Shei,

258
00:17:14,230 --> 00:17:16,300
I came as soon as I learned
of the situation.

259
00:17:16,300 --> 00:17:17,030
It seems my timing

260
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,440
is just right.

261
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:25,200
I knew it.

262
00:17:25,550 --> 00:17:26,829
You cunning Foxy Tang.

263
00:17:32,130 --> 00:17:32,720
Let's go.

264
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,400
I never expected the Vice-Chief Jiang

265
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,800
to be that kind of person.

266
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:48,550
Right?

267
00:17:48,910 --> 00:17:50,030
He always seemed

268
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:51,560
so loyal to the Sect Master.

269
00:18:15,650 --> 00:18:20,290
♪ I cross the Yan River in the wasteland ♪

270
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:17,920
His body

271
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:20,720
was completely dissolved by the poison.

272
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:21,750
All I could recover was this.

273
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:26,170
♪ Singing a long, unfinished song ♪

274
00:18:27,420 --> 00:18:32,370
♪ The full moon and a few shining stars ♪

275
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:29,680
You should go—

276
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:32,570
the ceremony on their side
is about to begin.

277
00:18:32,570 --> 00:18:37,130
♪ Look down on my dream ♪

278
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:35,920
Go bid your master a final farewell.

279
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:39,390
Master Jiang,

280
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:40,790
a year ago,

281
00:18:41,310 --> 00:18:42,640
Jiang Cheng was secretly fed

282
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:44,400
the Blood Ghost Pill by Jiang Qingyu.

283
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:49,190
♪ The breeze blows through the pleats ♪

284
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,160
He never guarded against

285
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,030
his own uncle

286
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:49,350
and remained completely unaware

287
00:18:49,350 --> 00:18:50,510
of the poisoning.

288
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:52,480
Cheng...

289
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:56,550
Then, half a year ago at Liulian Cottage,

290
00:18:55,920 --> 00:19:01,460
♪ Water polishes the old ruts ♪

291
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:59,440
