at his closest friend

296
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,400
in a hallucination.

297
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:10,330
Feng Chuanxiang, gravely wounded

298
00:19:10,550 --> 00:19:12,280
and knowing his time was short,

299
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:13,550
didn't want

300
00:19:13,550 --> 00:19:15,510
Jiang Cheng to live with the guilt
of killing his friend,

301
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:16,750
so he chose

302
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:18,670
to await death alone.

303
00:19:21,620 --> 00:19:22,550
When Jiang Cheng

304
00:19:22,910 --> 00:19:24,660
woke the next day,

305
00:19:24,690 --> 00:19:26,420
Feng Chuanxiang had vanished.

306
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:27,390
Tormented daily

