My Human Sword

580
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:32,510
is drawn only against villains—

581
00:32:32,510 --> 00:32:34,370
I acted out of necessity just now.

582
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:35,200
Wait,

583
00:32:35,610 --> 00:32:36,510
I'm from Camellia Island,

584
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:37,700
you're from Ranqing Sect—

585
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:39,110
we're both on the side of righteousness.

586
00:32:39,110 --> 00:32:40,710
Let's talk this through calmly.

587
00:32:40,710 --> 00:32:42,560
Ranqing Sect… they're all dead.

588
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,640
All of them!

589
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:45,350
What did you say?

590
00:32:45,350 --> 00:32:45,920
All dead?

591
00:32:46,110 --> 00:32:47,510
The entire Ranqing Sect?

592
00:32:52,550 --> 00:32:53,200
How?

593
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:55,510
Who did it?

594
00:32:56,350 --> 00:32:57,310
It was Tang Lici!

595
00:32:57,530 --> 00:32:58,160
He sent

596
00:32:58,160 --> 00:32:59,200
a demoness in red

597
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,400
and forced us to take large doses

598
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:01,640
of the Blood Ghost Pill…

599
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,840
I was the only one who…

600
00:33:55,750 --> 00:33:56,540
Look,

601
00:33:59,830 --> 00:34:00,680
isn't that the legendary

602
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:01,350
Master Puzhu?

603
00:34:01,350 --> 00:34:02,810
Isn't that Master Puzhu!?

604
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:05,130
I finally get to see him in person!

605
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:22,120
Thank you, Master Puzhu.

606
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,230
If not for you,

607
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:24,190
I would

608
00:34:24,190 --> 00:34:25,630
have shamed my sect today.

609
00:34:25,630 --> 00:34:27,920
Of the Three Swords—
Heaven, Earth, and Human—

610
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:29,710
you have begun to grasp the path
of the Human Sword.

611
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:30,570
It won't be long

612
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:33,110
before you reach the Earth Sword realm.

613
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:33,670
Really?

614
00:34:39,690 --> 00:34:41,350
Truly worthy of Master Puzhu—

615
00:34:41,570 --> 00:34:43,030
such grace and composure.

616
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:47,960
The killer's name

617
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,400
is Tang Lici.

618
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:10,920
Come in.

619
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:23,840
The Hao family massacre case
has been resolved.

620
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:25,480
Miss Zhong has already taken Jiang Qingyu

621
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:27,320
back to the Sword Alliance to report.

622
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:28,190
Shouldn't you

623
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,450
also return to Yanxian now?

624
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,280
Yes,

625
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:33,360
Mr. Tang.

626
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:36,760
Whenever it's convenient along the way,

627
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:38,800
you may drop me off at any pier.

628
00:35:40,470 --> 00:35:42,330
Why don't you say you wish to stay?

629
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:44,420
Are you willing to let me stay?

630
00:35:45,030 --> 00:35:45,800
Wasn't that

631
00:35:46,710 --> 00:35:48,310
your goal all along—to stay?

632
00:35:57,990 --> 00:36:00,590
The water is boiling.
I'll prepare tea for you.

633
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:10,480
You are not Chi Yun,

634
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:11,820
not my servant.

635
00:36:12,150 --> 00:36:13,550
You don't have to do this.

636
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:16,480
You've allowed me to stay,
even if temporarily.

637
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:18,230
I have little wealth to offer,

638
00:36:18,630 --> 00:36:20,550
so being able to help with small tasks

639
00:36:20,550 --> 00:36:21,800
puts my heart at ease.

640
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:35,030
You may look.

641
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,050
Thank you, Mr. Tang.

642
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:56,280
Master Jiang,

643
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:58,030
I must return promptly
to the Sword Alliance,

644
00:36:58,030 --> 00:36:59,490
so I'll take my leave here.

645
00:37:01,150 --> 00:37:02,550
The traitor Jiang Qingyu

646
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:04,480
is now in your hands, Ms. Zhong.

647
00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:05,360
I trust you will bring him

648
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:07,510
before the Central Plains Sword Alliance
for judgment.

649
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:08,170
Yanmen Sect

650
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:10,000
will also spare no effort in assisting

651
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:12,440
the investigation
into the Blood Ghost Pill case,

652
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:13,920
pursuing it to the very end.

653
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:14,520
Thank you.

654
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:16,610
In that case,

655
00:37:17,030 --> 00:37:18,290
let us each return to our duties

656
00:37:18,290 --> 00:37:19,290
and trust to fate.

657
00:37:34,230 --> 00:37:35,710
Who is that,

658
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:38,100
arriving with such grandeur?

659
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:40,440
The Sword King has arrived.

660
00:37:45,510 --> 00:37:46,370
The Sword King?

661
00:37:51,230 --> 00:37:52,590
Greetings, Sword King.

662
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:54,800
-Greetings, Sword King.
-Greetings, Sword King.

663
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:56,400
We were unaware of your arrival

664
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:58,190
and failed to greet you properly.

665
00:37:58,190 --> 00:37:59,670
Had we received word earlier,

666
00:37:59,670 --> 00:38:01,360
I would have prepared a banquet

667
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:03,150
in your honor, Sword King.

668
00:38:03,710 --> 00:38:05,360
Urgent matters take precedence.

669
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,630
I'm afraid there is no time

670
00:38:06,630 --> 00:38:08,430
to enjoy Yanmen's hospitality.

671
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:12,400
Might I ask what you mean by that,
Sword King?

672
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,760
The Blood Ghost Pill.

673
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:17,820
Hand over the prisoner Jiang Qingyu
at once.

674
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:19,600
Sword King Yu.

675
00:38:23,030 --> 00:38:24,840
No one may approach
the Sword King's presence.

676
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:25,640
Master Jiang,

677
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:28,670
if you have something to say,
speak from where you stand.

678
00:38:28,670 --> 00:38:29,190
Hold it!

679
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:32,320
This is still Jiang's territory.

680
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:33,630
Calling yourselves an orthodox sect,

681
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:35,160
you don't even know the simple courtesy
of a guest deferring to their host.

682
00:38:35,160 --> 00:38:36,920
Then do you understand
the principle of first come, first served?

683
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:37,670
If you want someone next time,

684
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:38,590
try waking up earlier

685
00:38:38,590 --> 00:38:40,190
and catching them yourself.

686
00:38:40,550 --> 00:38:41,400
Who are you

687
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,030
to act so insolently

688
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:44,450
before the Sword King?

689
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:48,590
Chi Yun, the Cloud.

690
00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:50,110
I never expected

691
00:38:50,150 --> 00:38:51,310
someone from the underworld

692
00:38:51,310 --> 00:38:53,910
to meddle in the affairs
of the righteous path.

693
00:38:54,230 --> 00:38:55,070
He knows me?

694
00:38:55,670 --> 00:38:57,670
The young master
of Yanmen consumed the Evil Pills;

695
00:38:57,670 --> 00:38:59,840
Master Jiang's own brother conspired
against his nephew.

696
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,670
A once-great sect has
not only bred traitors

697
00:39:01,670 --> 00:39:03,550
but also colluded with underworld figures.

698
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:04,920
To see Yanmen fall so low

699
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:06,550
is truly disheartening.

700
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:07,680
Sword King Yu,

701
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:09,770
this individual

702
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:10,990
has already been handed over

703
00:39:10,990 --> 00:39:12,590
to the Central Plains Sword Alliance
for judgment.

704
00:39:12,590 --> 00:39:13,520
That's correct,

705
00:39:16,190 --> 00:39:16,850
Sword King.

706
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,360
I am Zhong Chunji,

707
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:21,150
Branch Chief of the Shanfeng Branch,
Central Plains Sword Alliance.

708
00:39:21,150 --> 00:39:22,800
Taking the prisoner Jiang Qingyu
into custody

709
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:24,480
is under the direct order of my master.

710
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:26,360
I ask for your understanding, Sword King.

711
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:27,960
You wield Little Peach Blossom,

712
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:30,150
the seventh-ranked dagger
on the Roll of Renowned Blades.

713
00:39:30,150 --> 00:39:32,480
You are Shao Yanping's beloved disciple.

714
00:39:32,480 --> 00:39:33,140
Young lady,

715
00:39:33,590 --> 00:39:34,990
how is your master doing?

716
00:39:35,230 --> 00:39:36,440
My master is well.

717
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:38,510
Thank you for your concern, Sword King.

718
00:39:38,510 --> 00:39:39,440
But did you know?

719
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:41,760
Even if your master were here today,

720
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,240
he would not dare stand in my way.

721
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:47,690
Sword One, Sword Two—seize the prisoner.

722
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:48,190
-Yes!
-Yes!

723
00:39:48,190 --> 00:39:48,520
Wait!

724
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,410
From the sound of it,

725
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:53,280
you believe whoever has the strongest fist
makes the rules. Is that it?

726
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:55,630
The Sword King City has always
upheld virtue to persuade

727
00:39:55,630 --> 00:39:57,760
and martial prowess to eradicate evil.

728
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:59,400
Do you dare obstruct me?

729
00:40:00,230 --> 00:40:02,090
Look how full of yourself you are.

730
00:40:02,110 --> 00:40:04,280
I'll stand right here
and take one strike from you—

731
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:06,340
you still won't so much as scratch me.

732
00:40:07,710 --> 00:40:08,360
Mr. Chi.

733
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,600
Chi Yun, have you lost your mind?

734
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:12,280
Well, you scum.

735
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,280
Do you dare or not?

736
00:40:13,320 --> 00:40:14,880
If I take even one step back,
you can take him—

737
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:16,030
I won't say a word.

738
00:40:16,550 --> 00:40:17,960
But if you can't hurt me,

739
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,510
take your pretty-boy entourage

740
00:40:19,510 --> 00:40:20,240
and get lost.

741
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:22,840
Even Master Puzhu

742
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:26,000
would not dare utter such insolent words.

743
00:40:26,150 --> 00:40:28,070
Enough nonsense—
do you take the bet or not?

744
00:40:28,070 --> 00:40:29,320
Afraid I'll bully you?

745
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:30,710
I'll even turn my back—

746
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:31,650
dare you try?

747
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:41,510
Sword King Yu,

748
00:40:42,230 --> 00:40:44,150
Chi Yun is just speaking out of anger.

749
00:40:44,150 --> 00:40:45,080
Yes, Sword King.

750
00:40:45,130 --> 00:40:45,460
He—

751
00:40:45,780 --> 00:40:46,380
Very well.

752
00:41:01,650 --> 00:41:02,380
I accept it.

753
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,190
Chi Yun.

754
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,320
Foxy Tang.

755
00:41:41,110 --> 00:41:42,230
I knew it—

756
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,550
every time I'm about to have my moment,

757
00:41:43,550 --> 00:41:45,480
you show up to steal the spotlight.

758
00:41:56,620 --> 00:41:57,220
Foxy Tang,

759
00:41:58,290 --> 00:41:59,550
I bet him I wouldn't take
a single step back.
